OL,3,CIndian couple targeted in racist
OL,4,Cattack as hate incidents rocket
OL,6,FThe number of hate incidents against
OL,7,Fethnic minority groups in Northern
OL,8,FIreland is the highest since records
OL,9,Fbegan 20 years ago.
OL,11,FPSNI figures have revealed there were
OL,12,F1353 reports between April 2023 and
OL,13,FMarch 2024, that's 132 more incidents
OL,14,Fcompared to the previous year.
OL,16,FIn a geographic breakdown of the
OL,17,Ffigures, Belfast recorded almost half
OL,18,Fof the total race incidents.
