OL,3,CIndian couple targeted in racist
OL,4,Cattack as hate incidents rocket
OL,6,FAn Indian couple living in north
OL,7,FBelfast have told UTV that they now
OL,8,Flive in fear after their car windows
OL,9,Fwere smashed in last week.
OL,11,FThe health workers, who wished to
OL,12,Fremain anonymous, said: "We've never
OL,13,Ffound anyone showing any kind of such
OL,14,Fhatred or racism to our face but this
OL,15,Fwas really shocking and disappointing
OL,16,Fwhen we came to know that this was a
OL,17,Ftargeted crime."
