OL,6,FAna Chandran, who represents the
OL,7,FBelfast Asian Women's Academy, said:
OL,8,F"We've come here to work, we
OL,9,Fcontribute to society, we pay tax.
OL,10,FThis is our home and we are just like
OL,11,Feveryone else, we are equal. The only
OL,12,Fdifference is our skin colour."
OL,14,FNorth Belfast MP John Finucane visited
OL,15,Fthe couple in their north Belfast home
OL,16,Fto give reassurance that they would be
OL,17,Fsupported.
